crates/php-server/

# macOS AppleDouble / metadata sidecars. On the external work volume these are
# created next to every file; they confuse Serena's indexer and can be staged by
# accident. (The copies git itself writes under .git/objects are git-internal and
# not covered by .gitignore — `scripts/clean-appledouble.sh` clears those.)
._*
**/._*
.DS_Store

# phpt-run scratch artifacts: tests executed with a cwd of the repo ROOT write
# their temp fixtures next to it. Anchored to the root (leading /) ON PURPOSE —
# a bare *.gz would silently mask legitimate committed test fixtures anywhere in
# the tree (bz2/zip/finfo assets, gz oracle fixtures), which is exactly the
# class of file this project must never lose.
/*.tmp
/*.gz
/readgzfile_temp/
/1x1.jpg
/DataFile*.txt
/EmptyFile*.txt
